  "title": "Planner",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for monitoring and managing of WIP and customer backlog.</li>\n  <li>Plan daily production schedule for manufacturing execution and work with cross-functional team to meet SOD.</li>\n  <li>Manage customer demand forecast &amp; capacity allocation.</li>\n  <li>Acting as customer interface in providing daily operational updates to customers.</li>\n  <li>Improve capacity utilization through better device mix management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma / Degree in Engineering / Supply Chain / Business / Manufacturing or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years working experience</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, meticulous and able to work well with teams</li>\n  <li>Able to work effectively in a dynamic environment</li>\n</ul>",
